News.Title: Anya Polytech & Fertilizers: Shares List at 22% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Anya Polytech & Fertilizers shares debuted on NSE SME at ₹17.10, a 22.14% premium to the IPO price of ₹14. The stock reached the 5% upper circuit at ₹17.95. The company raised ₹44.80 crore through a fresh issue of 320 lakh shares.
